snippet.title: Courier Tale - Release Date Trailer | Delivering 10 September 2024!
snippet.description:
Courier Tale will be delivered to Steam on 10 September 2024! Play the prologue demo & wishlist Courier Tale on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1632100/Courier_Tale/

You've joined the gig economy as a courier for T.A.L.E. Couriers! Explore, meet and chat with a cast of characters, complete deliveries for the company while doing jobs on the side in this walkin' n talkin' pixel art adventure where this job is not everything you expected it to be...

https://www.x.com/couriertale  
https://www.instagram.com/couriertale  
htttps://www.facebook.com/couriertale  
https://www.couriertale.com
